Synopsis: Removes a file from a vector store.
Description: The Remove-OAIVectorStoreFile function removes a file from a vector store specified by the VectorStoreId and FileId parameters.

Examples.Title: EXAMPLE 1
Examples.Code:
Remove-OAIVectorStoreFile -VectorStoreId "12345" -FileId "67890"
Removes the file with ID "67890" from the vector store with ID "12345".
